dataset.title: Contours 2017
dataset.description:
This data set depicts countywide 1' contours derived from QL1 HD LiDAR in 2017. The data set is used for cartography, display and analysis. Elevations are expressed in NAVD88 vertical datum. This dataset is static and reflects conditions at the time of capture. Feature codes used in the data:

dataset.title: Parcels
dataset.description:
This layer depicts countywide land parcels in Calvert County, Maryland. The data is maintained in the Department of Technology Services with cooperation from the Department of Community Planning and Building. Attribute data is maintained monthly using a file downloaded from the Maryland State Department of Assessments and Taxation.

The data were originally developed from 600 scale tax maps. As newer plats and other information become available the parcel boundaries are being edited to reflect the more accurate data.
